//Siege class def file.

ClassInfo
{
	name				"Tat_RRebel"
	weapons				WP_BLASTER_PISTOL|WP_BLASTER|WP_MELEE|WP_CONC_NADE
	attributes			MB_ATT_PISTOL,2|MB_ATT_BLASTER,3|MB_ATT_DODGE,1|MB_ATT_AMMO,2|MB_ATT_ASSEMBLE,1|MB_ATT_STAMINA,2|MB_ATT_MICRO_GRENADES,1
	maxhealth			60
	maxarmor			20
	extralives			2
	speed				1.04
	model				"rebel" 				//this is optional, if it's here it forces the model to this.
	skin				"desert"					//this is optional, if it's here it forces the skin to this.
	uishader			"models/players/rebel/mb2_icon_desert"
	MBClass				MB_CLASS_CLONETROOPER
	resource			RESOURCE_STAMINA
	special1			EAS_HI_SPRINT
	special3			EAS_HI_DODGE
}

WeaponInfo0
{
	WeaponToReplace		WP_BLASTER     					//Required: Weapon Slot of weapon you're replacing
	WeaponBasedOff		WP_BLASTER      					//Required: For future use, should be the same as WeaponToReplace
	NewWorldModel		"models/weapons2/dh-17/dh-17_w.glm"  	//Required: New 3rd person/dropped weapon model
	NewViewModel		"models/weapons2/dh-17/dh-17_FA.md3"   	//Required: New 1st person weapon model
	Icon				"gfx/hud/w_icon_dh-17" 				//Required: Weapon change icon
	WeaponName			"DH-17 Blaster"    					//Required: Weapon change display name
}

description	"Rebel Soldier

^2Weaponry:
- Blaster Pistol (2)
- DH-17 Blaster (3)
- 1 Concussion Grenade

^8Attributes:
- Stamina (2)
- Reinforcements (2)
- Assemble (1)

^3Abilities:
- Sprint ^3[CS1]
- Dodge (1) ^3[CS3]

The men and women of the Rebel Alliance were fiercely dedicated to the principle of freedom, and would lay down their lives to win their objectives. Some were Imperials disillusioned with their government's tyranny."
